      "content": "thanks for that, it's a bit faster but i just tried running it on the test server and it's still timing out on the massive inputs (like n > 10^18). the grader is basically punishing anything that doesn't feel instantaneous. i really just need it to pass the runtime check so i can submit this. can u try something else that's way faster for those huge numbers?",
